 |isbn=0-85404-433-7
}}</ref>。這種使用下標的記法受SI官方出版物認可<ref name="BIPM_SI_units">{{SIbrochure|page=112}}</ref>，且與其它相關常數的記法相符，包括[[真空磁導率|真空磁導率]]''μ''<sub>0</sub>、[[真空電容率|真空電容率]]''ε''<sub>0</sub>（又稱電常數）以及[[自由空間阻抗|自由空間阻抗]]''Z''<sub>0</sub>。本條目以''c''代表真空中的光速。

自1983年起，[[國際單位制|國際單位制]]（{{lang|en|SI}}）將米定義為{{frac|1|{{val|299792458}}}}秒內光在真空中所運行的距離。因此，光速的精確值等於{{val|299792458|u=m/s}}<ref name="Boyes">{{Cite book
 |last=Sydenham
 |first=PH
 |year=2003
 |chapter=Measurement of length
 |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=sarHIbCVOUAC&pg=PA56
 |editor=Boyes, W
 |title=Instrumentation Reference Book
 |edition=3rd
 |page=56
 |publisher=Butterworth–Heinemann
 |isbn=0-7506-7123-8
 |quote=... if the speed of light is defined as a fixed number then, in principle, the time standard will serve as the length standard ...
 |access-date=2015-05-23
 |archive-date=2014-09-21
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921021130/http://books.google.com/books?id=sarHIbCVOUAC&pg=PA56
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref><ref name="Fundamental Physical Constants">{{cite web
 |title=CODATA value: Speed of Light in Vacuum
 |url=http://physics.nist.gov/cgi-bin/cuu/Value?c
 |work=The NIST reference on Constants, Units, and Uncertainty
 |publisher=[[國家標準技術研究所|NIST]]
 |accessdate=2009-08-21
 |archive-date=2017-06-25
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625090639/http://physics.nist.gov/cgi-bin/cuu/Value?c
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref><ref name="Jespersen">
{{Cite book
 |last=Jespersen |first=J |last2=Fitz-Randolph |first2=J |last3=Robb |first3=J
 |year=1999
 |title=From Sundials to Atomic Clocks: Understanding Time and Frequency
